The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, metal, soul
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, davidoff, bolivar, bluemaster
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, subway, train
 1. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the bolivar-smoker##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the bolivar-smoker and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person driving the train##1
 5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the bolivar-smoker is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | fantasy | family  | zombie  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo   | bolivar   | bluemaster | davidoff |
| Transport     | airplane    | train   | bike    | subway  |

