 7. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing domino is between the person playing monopoly and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
